## wild cards hands on 
1.  touch abc abcd abcde abcdef abcdefg adbdefgh
2. touch file1 file2 file3 file4 file5
3. ls -l
4. ls -l abc*
5. ls -l abcd* 
6. ls -l f*
7. rm abcd* 
8. rm f* 
9. touch heycat1 jumpcat2 sadcatkill laughcat123
10 rm *cat* 
11 rm a* 
12 rm f* 
13 touch abc{1..9}-xyz
14 ls -l *t 
15 ls -l ?cat 
16 rm ?cat 

* -> represent zero or more characters
? -> represent a single character 
[] -> represent a range of characters

